    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This car is the perfect canvas for someone who loves to bring a vehicle back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a fraction of the cost. If you're looking for a budget-friendly way to start your next automotive adventure, this is the one for you!",
