    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's easy on the wallet? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for the road! It shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone needing reliable transportation. With a bit of cosmetic TLC, this car will continue to serve you well for miles to come!",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car drives smoothly, with a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts precisely. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid, road-ready vehicle that requires no immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional acquisition for the discerning motorist: a vehicle maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits a level of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom character. Mechanically superlative and aesthetically pristine, this motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade offering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. If you're looking for a ride that's truly pristine and ready for a new home, this is the one! I'm super happy to chat or answer any questions you have\u2014let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated zenith. The S54 3.2L inline-six exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring surgical power delivery. The chassis remains factory-spec with a reinforced rear subframe and pristine bushings, maintaining the car's legendary torsional rigidity and steering linearity. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the cross-drilled rotors, functions with showroom-level precision. This is a turn-key investment for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    }
  ],
